DESCRIPTION:Event Name: Scribbr: Introductory Interview with Bruce Lam\n\nT
 hanks for taking the time to schedule a meeting with me. I am the recruiter
  for Scribbr and I am based in the United States. I look forward to speakin
 g with you about Scribbr and to learning about your career journey.\n\n\nFo
 r this initial call\, specifically I want to learn about your background in
 :\n\n1. Fullstack software engineering\n2. Performing autonomously on techn
 ical projects\n3. Optimizing applications to handle scaling\n4. Motivations
  for seeking a new role\n5. Interpersonal abilities (ie soft skills) in tea
 m settings\n\n\nFor this appointment\, you can choose to meet via a Zoom me
 eting or a Google Meeting. You can keep the camera on or off.\n\n\nLet me k
 now if you have any questions.\n\n\nSincerely\,\n\n\nBruce Lam\n\nSenior Re
 cruiter at Course Hero and Scribbr\n\nLocation: This is a Zoom web conferen
 ce.\n\nYou can join this meeting from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphon
 e.\nhttps://coursehero.zoom.us/j/92032933646\n\nOne tap mobile:\n+1 646 876
  9923\,\,92032933646#\n+1 646 931 3860\,\,92032933646#\n\nYou can also dial
  in using your phone.\nUS: +1 646 876 9923\, +1 646 931 3860\, +1 301 715 8
 592\, +1 305 224 1968\, +1 309 205 3325\, +1 312 626 6799\, +1 564 217 2000
 \, +1 669 444 9171\, +1 669 900 6833\, +16892781000\, +1 719 359 4580\, +1 
 253 205 0468\, +1 253 215 8782\, +1 346 248 7799\, +1 360 209 5623\, +1 386
  347 5053\, +1 507 473 4847\, +1 877 853 5247\, +1 888 788 0099\, +1 833 54
 8 0276\, +1 833 548 0282\nMeeting ID: 920-329-33646\n\nFind your local numb
 er: https://coursehero.zoom.us/u/aBy6Fw1Hi\n\nI understand and agree that p
 ersonal data provided in my CV and interview may be used solely for recruit
 ment purposes by Scribbr and will be kept on record for the duration of my 
 employment (if hired) or for a maximum period of 3 months. : I consent\n\nC
 hoose one (or more) of the boxes that accurately describes you. This will h
 elp me understand your priorities and needs as a job candidate. : I am not 
 in a hurry to start a new job but open to a new change\n\nNeed to make chan
 ges to this event?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/f73d353f-d9c
 7-4913-9ab1-ca08277bae95\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/f7
 3d353f-d9c7-4913-9ab1-ca08277bae95\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n
