DESCRIPTION:Hi Nikolai\,\n\nThanks for choosing a time for us to chat about
  the Senior Frontend Engineer (React) position. There's seems to be a syste
 m issue on our side so I re-sending the confirmation invite. The only chang
 e is the google meet link.\n\nYou're confirmed for your interview on:\n\nDa
 te/Time: May 3\, 2024 1:15pm-2:00pm CEST\nInterviewers: Jo-Ann Lim\n\nGoogl
 e Meet: https://meet.google.com/ubk-tfvf-owp\n\nDon't forget to add it to y
 our personal calendar.\nPlease note that we use BrightHire to record our in
 terviews. This allows us to focus more on the conversation and less on taki
 ng notes. If you do not want us to use BrightHire\, please reach out to you
 r recruiter.\n\nLet us know if you have any questions before your interview
 .\n\nKind Regards\,\nJo-Ann\n\nTalent Acquisition @ Creative Fabrica
