ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=NEEDS-ACTION;CN=Ru
 pert McKay;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:rupert.mckay@odido.nl
CREATED:20240308T093946Z
DESCRIPTION:Dear Nikolai\,\n\nAs discussed it is our pleasure to invite you
  for the deepdive into the code\, for the role of Software Engineer at Odid
 o!\n\nYou will have the deepdive with Rupert McKay (Principal Engineer Fron
 t-end) and Dmytro Shapovalov (Senior Software Engineer)\nYou can ask for Ru
 pert at the reception desk! You will also get a QR code sent to enter the b
 uilding!\n\n\nHere are some tips:\n\n  *   Talk out loud as you think. We w
 ill ask questions to prompt this\, but it is easier if we can hear your tho
 ughts and how you create your code.\n  *   Don't pretend to know something 
 you don't. It is ok not to know things. We are more likely to be impressed 
 if you ask for a hint\, and incorporate that hint well\, than if we get the
  sense that you are trying to bluff your way through.\n  *   Start simple. 
 We don't expect a perfectly formed answer right away. It is sensible to app
 roach any problem with a naive solution\, and to discuss its weaknesses\, b
 efore gradually working towards more advanced solutions.\n\n\nGood luck\, e
 njoy your weekend and again\, don’t forget to smile while coding!!\;-)\n\nR
 obin\n\n\n\n\nKind regards / Vriendelijke groet\,\n\nRobin Disma\nTalent Ac
 quisition Manager IT & Network\n+31 (0)6 18 07 4000\nE-mail robin.disma@odi
 do.nl<mailto:robin.disma@odido.nl>\n\n[cid:image001.gif@01DA713E.E1470550]\
 n\n\n\nOdido Netherlands bv\nWaldorpstraat 60 ● 2521 CC ● Den Haag\n\n[Afbe
 elding met symbool\, cirkel\, logo\, Lettertype  Automatisch gegenereerde b
 eschrijving]<http://www.x.com/odidonederland>  [A black and white logo  Des
 cription automatically generated with low confidence] <https://www.linkedin
 .com/company/odidonederland/>   [A white letter f in a circle  Description 
 automatically generated with medium confidence] <https://www.facebook.com/o
 didonederland/>   [A black and white logo  Description automatically genera
 ted with low confidence] <https://www.instagram.com/OdidoNederland/>\n\n\n\
 n\n\n\n\n__________________________________________________________________
