DESCRIPTION:Hi Nikolai\, <br><br>Thanks for making yourself available for a
  live tech talks at our office! <br><br>The interviews will mainly consist 
 of a <b>System Design Interview</b> with a whiteboard.<br><br>These session
 s will be held at our Headquarter (<b>Rijnzathe 16\, 7th floor\, 3454 PV Ut
 recht</b>) with Aleksandr Arakelov (Head of Software Engineering)\, Luc Uit
 dewilligen (Product Development Lead) and Jonas Weidner (Lead Software Engi
 neer).<br>Our office is reachable with busses 24 and 28 from Utrecht Centra
 l Station. <br><br>This is also an opportunity to get to know better our en
 vironment and product\, so feel free to share your questions\, attitude and
  overall personality\, we'll really appreciate it!<br><br>Should you need a
 ny further assistance\, please feel free to give me a call at:<table><tbody
 ><tr><td><a><u>+31 (0)614216288</u></a></td></tr></tbody></table><br>Or sen
 d me an email at <a href="mailto:w.morana@ampowr.com" target="_blank"><u><u
 ><u><u><u><u><u><u>w.morana@ampowr.com</u></u></u></u></u></u></u></u></a>.
 <br><br>I hope that's all for now! Thanks Nikolai and see you then!<br><br>
 <br>Have a great week.<br><br><br>Best\, <br>Walter Morana\n\nDeelnemen via
  Google Meet: https://meet.google.com/egh-wuek-tsf\nOf bel: (NL) +31 20 257
  3213 Pincode: 294550768#\nMeer telefoonnummers: https://tel.meet/egh-wuek-
 tsf?pin=7908925408342&hs=7\n\nGa voor meer informatie over Meet naar https:
 //support.google.com/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20240418T151535Z
