 hange at ValueBlue! 🐬\n\n\nYou can expect questions about your career mome
 nt and your past experiences as well as a deep dive into your career motiva
 tions and what engages you on a daily basis.\n\n\nOf course\, this is a two
 -sided conversation\, so I'll expect to be questioned by you as well. Here 
 you can check more about us<https://valueblue.com/> and our way of working<
 https://careers.valueblue.com/>\,\n\n\nSee you soon\,\n\nDan Bersagui\n\nLo
 cation: This is a Microsoft Teams web conference.\n\nYou can join this meet
 ing from your computer\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://teams.microsoft.c
