CREATED:20240228T082929Z
DESCRIPTION:Hi Nikolai\,\n\nAs discussed\, it is our pleasure to invite you
  for the first tech screening for the role of Software Engineer Front-end w
 ithin Odido NL!\n\nYou will have the screening with Rupert McKay (Principal
  Engineer).\n\nThis screening will be a quick scan on code. Here are some t
 ips:\n\n* Talk out loud as you think. We will ask questions to prompt this\
 , but it is easier if we can hear your thoughts and how you create your cod
 e.\n* Don't pretend to know something you don't. It is ok not to know thing
 s. We are more likely to be impressed if you ask for a hint\, and incorpora
 te that hint well\, than if we get the sense that you are trying to bluff y
 our way through.\n* Start simple. We don't expect a perfectly formed answer
  right away. It is sensible to approach any problem with a naive solution\,
  and to discuss its weaknesses\, before gradually working towards more adva
 nced solutions.\n\nGood luck and don’t forget to smile while coding! 🙂\n\n
 Ana\n\nKind regards / Vriendelijke groet\,\n\nAna Gancearuc\n\nTalent Acqui
 sition Sourcer\n\n+373 69 19 71 81\n\nE-mail ana.gancearuc@odido.nl<mailto:
 ana.gancearuc@odido.nl>\n\n\n[https://res.cdn.office.net/assets/mail/file-i
 con/png/pdf_16x16.png]Software Engineer Front 4.pdf<https://tmnlso-my.share
 point.com/:b:/g/personal/ana_gancearuc_odido_nl/EdD-5FfULK5PlYu2QDqU2kYBopb
 7HfC_aLnzfl6TzqNFzg>\n\n\n_________________________________________________
 _______________________________\nMicrosoft Teams meeting\nJoin on your comp
 uter\, mobile app or room device\nClick here to join the meeting<https://te
 ams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_NmVhMTdjZDctMzllMy00NmIwLTgzZT
 gtMjdmNzE3NTZlZDQ3%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22Tid%22%3a%2263a8df83-063c-43
 12-a508-dc01b7508661%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%22255e2f9c-3830-42a7-8564-1e284b58b9
 a6%22%7d>\nMeeting ID: 327 527 025 136\nPasscode: mzBruW\nDownload Teams<ht
 tps://www.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-teams/download-app> | Join on the w
 eb<https://www.microsoft.com/microsoft-teams/join-a-meeting>\n[https://prdd
 ata001.blob.core.windows.net/cdncontainer/o-teams_image.png]\nLearn More<ht
 tps://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting> | Meeting options<https://teams.microsoft.co
 m/meetingOptions/?organizerId=255e2f9c-3830-42a7-8564-1e284b58b9a6&tenantId
 =63a8df83-063c-4312-a508-dc01b7508661&threadId=19_meeting_NmVhMTdjZDctMzllM
 y00NmIwLTgzZTgtMjdmNzE3NTZlZDQ3@thread.v2&messageId=0&language=en-US>\n____
 ___________________________________________________________________________
 _\n
